{
  "texts": [
    "The initial search phase used Google Scholar's search function to identify relevant articles based on combinations of XR-related terms and privacy and safety keywords.",
    "Initial search terms included:",
    "• Extended reality privacy • Extended reality safety • Virtual reality privacy • Virtual reality safety • Augmented reality privacy • Augmented reality safety • Mixed reality privacy • Mixed reality safety",
    "We read the titles and abstracts of returned articles and filtered them for relevance based on whether they substantively discussed privacy or safety related to IXR.",
    "Our inclusion criteria for risks are those that have manifested in the physical world or existing Internet and are technologically plausible considering the current technolog-ical trajectory of IXR, as well as novel risks that are technologically plausible."
  ]
}